Package: owncloud-sync
Version: 0.1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libdbus-1-3, libsecret-1-0
Suggests: python3-nautilus
Maintainer: ownCloud Sync Contributors <desktop@owncloud.com>
Description: ownCloud Desktop Sync Client
 Syncs files between your computer and an ownCloud Infinite Scale server.
 Includes shell integration for Nautilus and Dolphin file managers.
